<h1> Create a new review</h1>

<p>Our users enable us to better one another's learning. Please be honest with your review in order for people to benefit from the most awesome resources!</p>

<form action="/reviews" method="POST">
  Review Title:<input class="input-block" type="text" name="title" placeholder="Amazing, Awful..." maxlength="60"><br>
  Rating:<input class="input-block" type="number" name="rating" min="0" max="5"><br>
  Content:<textarea class="content-input" type="text" name="content" maxlength="800"></textarea><br>
  <input class="btn" type="submit" value="Submit">
  <input type="hidden" name="resource_id" value="{{resource_id}}">
</form>
